Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi Pi Po Pe Pa Po Pa Po
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什麼？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi Po Po Pi Pa Pu Pe Pa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Po Pa Pa Pe Po Po Pa Pu Pu Pi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa Pa Pi Pu Po Po Pi Pu Pa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pe Po Po Pa Pe Pa Pe Pu Po
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 阿哈... 阿呵...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bo... BoBi~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:57.98,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs58\blur12\fad(700,800)\3c&HE29C3F&\shad0\3a&H01&\pos(951,569)}男子高中生與老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別揮這麼用力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要用高爾夫球桿打啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 父親 來玩玩傳球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛 再玩一下高爾夫球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是高爾夫球嗎？ 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣 爸爸小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可曾經夢想成為飛行員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高爾夫跟棒球八竿子打不著啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 父子玩傳球 長大就放牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呸...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就把這個外套捲起來當球用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個老梗就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡 將來有想要做些什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出國什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去幫助更多的人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做的到嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這麼說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 原來你們在這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊... 勇介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡門鎖住進不去 鑰匙借我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有鑰匙 我們就不會在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽去旅遊了 還有三天才會回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男子高中生的日常由以上贊助商提供
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栗子樹下...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊助播出
